        <description xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">These spinach and feta turkey burgers are a big hit in the summertime when everyone is tired of the same old hamburgers and hot dogs. Serve with or without buns and your favorite condiments. I like to serve these with lettuce, tomato, and tzatziki sauce.</description>
        <subject xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:resource="http://example.org/auto/Main%20Course"/>
